OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain moving eastwards
OL,7,Fthrough the evening and overnight.
OL,8,FTending to become drier by dawn with
OL,9,Fsome clearer spells developing.
OL,10,FAnother muggy night to come.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA cloudy start with some
OL,13,Fspots of rain, especially over the
OL,14,Fhills. The cloud will break up
OL,15,Fthroughout the morning, leading to a
OL,16,Fmuch brighter afternoon. Feeling a
OL,17,Ftouch fresher.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
